  "decision_conditions": [
    "Insufficient and inadequate information has been provided to demonstrate that there is no demand for the office foorspace. The proposal is therefore contrary to policy ED1 of the Lambeth Local Plan 2021.",
    "The proposed development is not car free. The proposed residential car parking within an area of excellent public transport accessibility (PTAL score of 6a) is contrary to Policy T6 of the Lambeth Local Plan 2021 and Policy T6 of the London Plan 2021.",
    "Insufficient information has been provided to demonstrate that a high standard of sustainable design and construction can be achieved as required by policy EN4 of the Lambeth Local Plan 2021 and SI1, SI2 and SI3 of the London Plan 2021.",
    "Insufficient information has been provided to demonstrate that the proposed development would contribute positively to actively reducing food risk through avoidance, reduction, management and mitigation. In the absence of this information the proposal is contrary to Policy EN5 of the Lambeth Local Plan 2021.",
    "In the absence of a s106 agreement to secure (i) Car permit free development; (ii) Car Club membership for a period of 3 years for the future residents and (iii) Cycle Hire membership for a period of 3 years for the future residents, the proposed development has the potential to unacceptably impact on the local highway network. The proposal fails to comply with policies T3 and T6 of the Lambeth Local Plan 2021 and T6 of the London Plan 2021."
  ],
